         <div subtype="original" type="letter" xml:id="L.8264" xml:lang="de">
            <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
            <dateline>[DEUTSCHE REICHSPOST. POSTKARTE HALLE a. S. 16.2.88]</dateline>
            <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
            <p> Recurrente poste chartam vestram respondens, valde gaudeo, quod forse vos visurus ero Romae. Ero Romae<note n="1" place="foot" type="editorial">
                  <bibl>
                     <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.bibliography#BIBL.1600"> Wolf, <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">Nachlaß</hi>, 632 </ref>
                  </bibl>, weist für 1888 nur einen Aufenthalt Schuchardts in <placeName ref="[authorityLink]"> Bologna</placeName> (Juni) nach. </note> totum per mensem, ab circa 15.-20. Martio usque ad finem Aprilis, domicilians in Monte citorio, et in hospitio quod vocant Albergo Milano. Nunc det D. O. M.<note n="2" place="foot" type="editorial">
                  <foreign xml:lang="la">„Deus Optimus Maximus“.</foreign>
               </note> ut nos videamus sani! </p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Amicissimus</salute>
               <signed>
                  <persName ref="[authorityLink]">
K.</persName>
               </signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
               <p> Halis Saxonum 16/12/83 </p>
            </postscript>
